'''''Star Wars: Return of the Jedi''''' is a comic series published by [[Marvel Comics]] that adapted [[Star Wars: Episode VI Return of the Jedi|''Star Wars'': Episode VI ''Return of the Jedi'']] into comic form and was published in [[1983]]. The series was republished as [[Classic Star Wars: Return of the Jedi (comic series)|''Classic Star Wars: Return of the Jedi'']] in [[1994]], and reprinted many times since then.

